title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
EB: The system should not display an out of sync message when overwriting the exported jar file in the given scenario.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Open a project in the software
2. Export the project directory as a jar
3. Place the exported jar file in the same directory
4. Attempt to overwrite the exported jar file for the second time
